    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how pristine this ride is. It's been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and pampered since day one. It looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014seriously, not a single scratch or smudge to be found! I'm only letting it go because I'm downsizing, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely fall in love with it. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
